divs: Sighting Details A Triangle shaped light in the sky appeared in front of the little dipper and moved west of that position and hoovered for about an hour. I went inside for a few minutes and returned to find it was gone. On photos it was the only light appearing in the sky in the photo. As a photo appears to be multicolor light, but round and blurry.
Summary: Triangle shape light in the sky.
